folder: Bainbridge Avenue & Fordham Road (East), Bronx, NY
text:
2556 Bainbridge Ave., east side, between East Fordham Road, and East 193rd Street, showing W.P.A. workmen building an addition to the rear of the Fordham Branch of the New York Public Library on Marion Ave. After completion the library will extend from Bainbridge to Marion Aves.
May 12, 1936.
Works Progress Administration.
Federal Art Project photo.
